headline: How AI could upend shopping
summary: AI is reshaping holiday shopping as consumers seek personalized gift ideas and deals from sites such as ChatGPT. Retailers such as Walmart and Target on the other hand are scrambling to stay ahead of the technology to help increase traffic ahead of the holiday season.
